oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Cover of a reunion account of the Thirtieth Anniversary of 68th Ohio Volunteers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The small booklet commemorated the 30th anniversary of the organization of the 68th Ohio Vol. Inf. at Napoleon, Ohio, and belonged to Pvt. Michael Wyrick, Co. G, 68th Ohio Vol. Inf., USA. Wyrick was not able to attend, and was listed as being in Waldron, Mich. 152 other members of the 68th were present, including 11 members of Wyrick's Co. G.
